--- min / max of Tuple ---
(0,'b')	(2,'c')
--- min / max of Array ---
[0,5]	[3,4]
--- min / max of Map ---
{'a':0,'b':5}	{'a':2,'b':3}
--- min / max of Decimal ---
-0.5	3.2
--- min / max of IPv4 / IPv6 ---
1.1.1.1	192.168.1.1
::1	2001:db8::1
--- any_value of Tuple (order-stable via ORDER BY) ---
(1,'a')
(3,'c')
--- argMin / argMax on Tuple value, numeric key ---
(2,'b')
(3,'c')
--- argMin / argMax on Array value ---
[3,4]
[3,4]
--- merge via GROUP BY (multi-partition) ---
1	(2,'b')	(1,'a')	(1,'a')	(2,'b')
2	(4,'d')	(3,'c')	(3,'c')	(4,'d')
--- empty / null handling ---
(0,'')	(0,'')	(0,'')	(0,'')	(0,'')	(0,'')
--- Nullable(Int32) aggregates (min/max only; any/anyLast are non-deterministic) ---
1	3	2	1
--- min/max over LowCardinality String ---
apple	zebra
--- min over nested Array(Tuple) ---
[(0,'c')]	[(2,'b')]
